---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="Retaining Walls Berwick VIC | Sleeper, Block & Concrete | Free Quote"
  description="Specialist retaining wall builders in Berwick. From Berwick Springs to Berwick Waters and the older established streets. Free fixed-price quotes — call (03) 9003 0223."
  canonical="https://pakenhamretainingwalls.com.au/berwick/">

  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-inner">
      <span class="hero-eyebrow">Berwick VIC 3806</span>
      <h1>Retaining walls across <span class="accent">Berwick</span>.</h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">
        From the older established streets near Berwick Village to the newer Berwick Springs
        and Berwick Waters estates, we build retaining walls and earthworks across the entire
        Berwick area.
      </p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a class="btn btn-primary" href="tel:+61390030223">&#9742; Call (03) 9003 0223</a>
        <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="/quote/">Get a free quote</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <span class="section-eyebrow">Berwick specifics</span>
      <h2>Two Berwicks &mdash; two retaining wall problems.</h2>
      <div class="divider"></div>

      <div style="max-width: 60rem;">
        <h3>Old Berwick (north of the Princes Highway)</h3>
        <p>
          The streets around Berwick Village &mdash; High Street, Manuka Road, Inglis Road &mdash;
          have larger established blocks, often with mature trees, bluestone outcrops, and
          long-standing retaining walls reaching the end of their service life. Most of the
          jobs we do here are <strong>replacements</strong>: tearing out a 30-year-old timber
          wall that&rsquo;s leaning and putting in concrete sleepers.
        </p>

        <h3 style="margin-top: 2rem;">New Berwick (Berwick Springs, Berwick Waters)</h3>
        <p>
          The newer estates around Clyde Road and the wetlands have flatter blocks but more
          fence-line walls between neighbours, plus more pools and outdoor entertaining areas
          that need short walls. Permits in Cardinia Shire (post-2015 estates) are stricter
          than the older City of Casey approvals &mdash; we handle the lodgement.
        </p>

        <h3 style="margin-top: 2rem;">Common Berwick retaining wall jobs</h3>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Replacement walls</strong> &mdash; old leaning timber to new concrete sleeper, same line, same height.</li>
          <li><strong>Pool surround walls</strong> &mdash; usually under 1m, no permit, but engineered to hold up against pool deck loads.</li>
          <li><strong>Boundary fence walls</strong> &mdash; short walls under fence lines where one block is higher than the next.</li>
          <li><strong>Garden bed walls</strong> &mdash; decorative timber or block walls under 600mm for landscaped beds and tiered gardens.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section-alt">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <h2>Wall types we build in Berwick.</h2>
      <div class="svc-grid">
        <a class="svc-card" href="/services/timber-retaining-walls/"><h3>Timber sleeper</h3><p>Most economical, 15&ndash;40 year lifespan.</p><span class="svc-link">Details &rarr;</span></a>
        <a class="svc-card" href="/services/concrete-sleeper-walls/"><h3>Concrete sleeper</h3><p>50+ year lifespan, ideal for taller walls.</p><span class="svc-link">Details &rarr;</span></a>
        <a class="svc-card" href="/services/block-retaining-walls/"><h3>Block / masonry</h3><p>Premium look, long lifespan.</p><span class="svc-link">Details &rarr;</span></a>
        <a class="svc-card" href="/services/excavation-earthworks/"><h3>Earthworks</h3><p>Cut-and-fill, drainage, levelling.</p><span class="svc-link">Details &rarr;</span></a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="cta-block">
        <h2>Berwick site visit &mdash; free.</h2>
        <p>Book a free measure-up and fixed-price quote.</p>
        <div class="hero-actions" style="justify-content:center;">
          <a class="btn btn-primary" href="tel:+61390030223">&#9742; Call (03) 9003 0223</a>
          <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="/quote/">Quote online</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
